Revision history for RPi-Gyro-MPU6050

0.01 UNREL
    - Auto generated distribution with Dist::Mgr
    - Added the OO Perl interface; pure Perl, with the I2C transport
      provided by RPi::I2C
    - Added accel(), gyro(), temp(), tilt(), accel_range(), gyro_range(),
      calibrate_gyro(), gyro_offsets(), sleep(), wake(), reset(),
      register() and close()
    - Added hardware-free parameter validation and mocked register file
      logic test suites
    - Added examples/imu.pl and examples/tilt.pl
    - Added the TECHNICAL INFORMATION POD section with the MPU-6050
      register map, scaling tables, sample rate/filter, clocking and
      power details
    - Limited CI to Linux runners; RPi::I2C is a Linux-only XS dependency
